      <scopecontent id="aspace_0a80bd7b864b2b8322961b5cf0304224">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>Letters between Sarah Buckingham and family and friends, and between other family members and friends. Among the letters from Clark Nettleton to his sister Mrs. Goodsell is an 1858 view of Saint Paul, Minnesota on letterhead.</p>  
